&lt;p&gt;You will lead high-impact strategic engagements, facilitate executive workshops, uncover opportunities for growth, and work across multidisciplinary teams to develop integrated strategies that influence business decisions, not just communications plans.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a leadership role for someone who enjoys asking better questions, connecting disparate ideas, and helping organizations navigate transformation.&lt;/p&gt;
